  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, your flesh becomes as hard as stone, giving you&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Damage-Reduction\">DR</a>&nbsp;10/<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/special-materials#TOC-Adamantine\">adamantine</a>, and you become immune to petrification. You suffer no penalties while squeezing through tight spaces and are immune to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Bull-Rush\">bull rush</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Drag\">drag</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Grapple\">grapple</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reposition\">reposition</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Trip\">trip</a>&nbsp;maneuvers, and to push and pull effects as long as you are standing on the ground.</p>"
